 To achieve a device info style with white background, you can follow these steps:

1. Use a suitable theme:
   For a white background, you can use a simple CSS rule like this:

```css
QGroupBox {
    background-color: white;
}
```

Note: In HTML/CSS, 'white' should be written as `#FFFFFF`. Replace `white` in the CSS snippet above.

2. Set other styles as per the given image's details.

Here is an example of a complete QGroupBox stylesheet:

```css
QGroupBox {
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    border-style: solid;
    border-width: 1px;
    padding: 10px;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #333;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

/* Custom Styles
